### JWT token authentication and authorization test cases

### 1. Generate a token for testing (simulate authentication)
# Copy the token value from the response (field "token")
POST {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/test/simulate-auth

### 2. Request to a protected method (with token)
# Replace <TOKEN> with the obtained value
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/test/protected
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 3. Request to a protected method (without token)
# Expected 401 Unauthorized
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/test/protected

### 4. Request to a public method
# Expected 200 OK
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/test/unauthorized

### Authentication and Authorization Test Cases

### 5. Register a new user
POST {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tester4",
  "email": "tester4@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### 6. Register a user with an existing email (should fail)
# Expected 409 Conflict
POST {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "OtherUser",
  "email": "tester4@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### 7. Login with valid credentials
POST {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tester4@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### 8. Login with invalid password (should fail)
# Expected 401 Unauthorized
POST {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tester4@example.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 9. Verify CurrentUserService (Authenticated)
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/test/whoami
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### To-Do Items Management Test Cases

### 10. Create a new to-do item (Authenticated)
# Expected: 201 Created with created item in response body and Location header
# @name createTodo
POST {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Another Test Todo",
  "description": "Another test description. Big description for testing purposes."
}

### 11. Create a to-do item without authentication (Anonymous)
# Expected: 401 Unauthorized
POST {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Anonymous Todo",
  "description": "Should not be created"
}

### 12. Create a to-do item with invalid payload (Missing title)
# Expected: 400 Bad Request
POST {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "This payload has an empty title"
}

### 13. Get a single to-do item by ID
# Expected: 200 OK with the requested item
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos/{{CreatedTodoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 14. Get a non-existent to-do item (or owned by another user)
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 15. Get a paginated list of to-do items
# Expected: 200 OK with "items", "totalCount", "page", and "pageSize" fields
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 16. Update an existing to-do item
# Expected: 200 OK with the updated item in the response body
PUT {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos/{{CreatedTodoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated API Implementation Title",
  "description": "Updated description for the manual tests"
}

### 17. Update a non-existent to-do item (or owned by another user)
# Expected: 404 Not Found
PUT {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ghost Update",
  "description": "Should fail because item does not exist"
}

### 18. Delete an existing to-do item
# Expected: 204 No Content
DELETE {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos/{{CreatedTodoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 19. Verify the item was deleted (Get by ID again)
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos/{{CreatedTodoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 20. Delete a non-existent to-do item (or owned by another user)
# Expected: 404 Not Found
DELETE {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### To-Do Items Filtering and Sorting Test Cases

### 21. Get list with filtering by title
# Expected: 200 OK, only items containing "Test" in the title
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos?title=Test&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 22. Get list with sorting by title (ascending)
# Expected: 200 OK, items sorted alphabetically by title (A-Z)
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos?sortBy=title&sortDescending=false&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 23. Get list with sorting by title (descending)
# Expected: 200 OK, items sorted alphabetically by title (Z-A)
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos?sortBy=title&sortDescending=true&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

### 24. Get list with combined filtering and sorting
# Expected: 200 OK, filtered results ("Test") sorted by title descending
GET {{ToDoList.Api_HostAddress}}/api/todos?title=Test&sortBy=title&sortDescending=true&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}